OL,7,FThe Speaker of the House of Commons
OL,8,Fhas revealed he received death threats
OL,9,Ffollowing .
OL,11,F's future in the role was seen as
OL,12,Fbeing under threat after the episode
OL,13,Fdescended into chaos.
OL,15,FThe 66-year-old, who was first elected
OL,16,Fas a Labour MP but relinquished party
OL,17,Faffiliation following his election as
OL,18,FSpeaker, was accused of partisanship
OL,19,Fby helping party leader Sir Keir
OL,20,FStarmer avoid an internal row.
