OL,7,FQuestioned about the affair by ITV
OL,8,FGranada Reports, the MP for Chorley
OL,9,Fsaid he had not received any death
OL,10,Fthreats during other contentious
OL,11,Ftimes, such as the Iraq war.
OL,13,FHe vowed to continue doing his job:
OL,14,F"I've got the majority of parliament
OL,15,Fbacking me all the way through.
OL,17,F"I will continue. It is for others to
OL,18,Fdecide my fate, not for me."
